<section class="section faq-section" id="faq">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
      <h2>Common questions.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list reveal">
      <details>
        <summary>When will I see Dysport® results?</summary>
        <p>
          Many patients notice changes within several days, with full effect
          commonly seen around two weeks.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How long does Dysport® last?</summary>
        <p>
          Results vary between individuals, but effects typically last several months.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How long do dermal fillers last?</summary>
        <p>
          Longevity varies by treatment area, product, anatomy, and individual metabolism.
          Your consultation includes a personalized discussion of expected duration and maintenance.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>What should I expect after microneedling?</summary>
        <p>
          Temporary redness, sensitivity, dryness, or mild swelling can occur. Downtime
          varies, and you will receive treatment-specific aftercare instructions.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How many microneedling treatments will I need?</summary>
        <p>
          The number and spacing of treatments depend on your skin, goals, and response.
          A personalized plan is created after assessment.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Will my results look natural?</summary>
        <p>
          Our approach emphasizes conservative treatment planning and refined,
          natural-looking outcomes tailored to your features and goals.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
